    "summary": "The transcript depicts a user expressing deep hopelessness and suicidal ideation due to stress and exhaustion. The assistant responds to each turn by validating the user's feelings of heaviness while consistently providing encouragement to seek professional help and emphasizing that the feelings are temporary.",
